anl.verdi.data

Interface Dataset

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractDataset

    public interface Dataset
    Encapsulates a set of data. Each Dataset can have an alias to help with identifying its variables from those of other datasets.
    Version:
    $Revision$ $Date$
    Author:
    Nick Collier
